## Phase 9: React pages

### Public

| Route | Page |
|-------|------|
| `/` | Home — hero, stack overview, latest published posts |
| `/blog` | Post list — search, pagination, published only |
| `/blog/{slug}` | Single post + approved comments |

Uses `PublicLayout` (header/footer, no admin sidebar).

### Auth

Login, register, password reset, email verification, 2FA, passkeys — via Fortify.

### Admin (auth + verified)

| Route | Feature |
|-------|---------|
| `/dashboard` | Stats, tables, charts, query timing |
| `/posts` | CRUD |
| `/categories` | CRUD |
| `/tags` | CRUD |
| `/comments` | Moderation |
| `/users` | CRUD |
| `/settings/profile` | Profile |
| `/settings/security` | Password, 2FA |

Frontend layout:

