## Quick start

```bash
composer install
cp .env.example .env
php artisan key:generate
php artisan migrate:fresh --seed
php artisan db:seed-heavy --no-interaction   # optional
npm install
npm run dev
php artisan serve
```

Demo login: `test@example.com` / `password`

- App: http://localhost:8000
- GraphQL: http://localhost:8000/graphql
- GraphiQL: http://localhost:8000/graphiql

